[
  {
    "scene": "TitleScene",
    "file": "01-title.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "歡迎來到美少女梗圖劇場第七集！AI 時代求生。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "小雪、小月和小樱面對人工智能的全面入侵，發現人類的生存危機不是 AI 太聰明，而是自己太依賴 AI。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "JokeScene1",
    "file": "02-joke1.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "小雪發現小月和小樱都在用 AI 寫作業。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "小月！你的報告怎麼寫了三十頁？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我叫 ChatGPT 幫我擴寫。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "擴寫？你原本寫了幾頁？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "三行。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "三行變三十頁？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我說「請詳細擴寫」，它真的很詳細。連參考文獻都幫我編了十七篇。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "那你交了嗎？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "當然沒有。教授問我參考文獻的作者，我一個都叫不出來。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoying",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "其實……我也用 AI 寫了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "小樱也？！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoying",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我的 AI 很貼心，幫我在結尾加了「本報告由 AI 輔助撰寫」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "至少你的 AI 有良心。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "JokeScene2",
    "file": "03-joke2.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "小雪設定 AI 自動回訊息，結果比本人更受歡迎。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "好了！我設定了 AI 自動回訊息。以後再也不用煩惱要回什麼了！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你確定？上次你用自動回覆，跟你媽說「收到，感謝您的反饋」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "那是意外！我重新訓練過了。現在它會模仿我的語氣。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoying",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "小雪……你 AI 剛才回了我一個「好的呢～♡」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "怎麼了？那是我平常的語氣啊。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoying",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "可是你剛才問我「今天晚上吃什麼」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你的 AI 比你還有禮貌。它甚至會加「辛苦了」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "最慘的是，我男友說他比較喜歡 AI 回的訊息。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoying",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……那是不是代表，你的存在被 AI 取代了？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "小樱！你不准說實話！"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "JokeScene3",
    "file": "04-joke3.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "小月發現有人用深度偽造技術做了她的假影片。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你們看這個影片。這是我嗎？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "哇，真的好像你！你在做什麼？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我在……跳抖音。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你會跳舞嗎？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "不會。這是深度偽造。有人用我的照片做了假的影片。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoying",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "那你怎麼辦？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我也用 AI 做了一個假的自己。讓那個假的去跳舞，真的我在家睡覺。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "等等，這樣你不就變成 AI 了嗎？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "不，我還是真人。只是我的「數位分身」替我工作。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoying",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "那如果大家都有數位分身，真人是不是就不用出門了？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "理論上是的。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "太好了！以後數位小雪去上課，真的小雪在家追劇！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "然後你的數位分身考了第一名。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……那我就更不想出門了。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "JokeScene4",
    "file": "05-joke4.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "三人討論在 AI 時代，人類到底還有什麼存在的意義。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "AI 會寫程式、會畫畫、會寫小說、會作曲。人類還能做什麼？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "人類還能……吃飯！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "AI 不需要吃飯。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "人類還能……睡覺！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "AI 不需要睡覺，而且二十四小時工作。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoying",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "人類還能……犯錯。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……這倒是真的。AI 不會犯錯。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "等等，小樱這個說法好深。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoying",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我不是在說深奧的話。我只是說，我昨天把鹽當糖加了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "但她說得對。AI 的完美反而讓它沒有靈魂。人類之所以有趣，就是因為我們會犯蠢。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "對！AI 永遠不會在半夜三點買一堆不需要的東西！"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "也不會在社群媒體上發布後悔的動態。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoying",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "更不會把密碼設成「123456」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoxue",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……小樱，你的密碼是 123456 嗎？"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoying",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "不是。是「123456789」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "xiaoyue",
        "voice": "vivian",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "vivian",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "比原來的還糟。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "OutroScene",
    "file": "06-outro.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "感謝收看美少女梗圖劇場第七集！AI 時代求生。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "AI 可以幫我們寫作業、回訊息、做影片，但有一件事 AI 永遠做不到——那就是像小雪一樣在半夜買不需要的東西。人類的不完美，才是我們最可愛的地方。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "serena",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "serena",
          "gender": "female",
          "accent": "Taiwan Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "下集預告：三人踏入了加密貨幣的世界。小雪投資了一萬塊買了一個叫「狗狗幣超級無敵版」的虛擬貨幣。小月冷靜分析後發現，這個幣的官網是用 Canva 做的。"
      }
    ]
  }
]
